Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:14.97,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\blur1\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:15.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:19.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:23.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:26.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:30.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:33.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:36.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:40.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:44.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:48.40,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:51.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:54.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:00:59.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:02.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:11.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:14.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:16.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:19.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.91,0:01:23.14,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\3c&HCADDFD&\c&H12130D&}Shirakawa Optics\NResearch Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.31,0:02:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What a horrifying\Nthing we've created.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But its announcement will\Nbe your ticket to fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.41,0:02:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No... we can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't plan to announce this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.27,0:02:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an amazing opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shibata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What if it were to fall\Ninto the wrong hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans invariably find a way to misuse\Nany valuable scientific achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're going to abandon\Nyour invention entirely?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A scientist cannot\Nbury his own invention.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be like\Nkilling his own child.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.43,0:02:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we print all the formulas\Nand blueprints on microfilm
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:02:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and seal it away somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our only\Nchoice, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where shall we hide it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better not tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't tell anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,about this laser.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:36.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But his assistant, Shibata,\Ndidn't come to work the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:42.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was secretly a member of Shocker's\Nworldwide information network.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I will convert you into a\Nglorious Shocker commander
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and grant you a special mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You are now my loyal\Nwarrior, Yamogerus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:18.06,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFCFFFE&\b1\pos(490.495,236.833)}The Murderous Yamogerus
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.77,0:04:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, go! Test your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Climb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:04:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Jab!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Jab, jab!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Left! Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Another jab! Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Jab, jab!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Jab, right! Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Jab!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Jab, jab!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The test was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's race!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that reckless driving...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They're chasing that car!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you people want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with us,\Nto a Shocker outpost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:23.43,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\3c&H527080&\c&H12130D&\bord4}Shirakawa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't know\Nwhy they'd be after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know why your assistant\Nbefore me quit abruptly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I care about\Nsomeone who's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But those people...\NShocker, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They said something strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're just going to quibble with\Nme, you can quit, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Machiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A m-monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be those\Npeople from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Shirakawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything in your\Nresearch that they might be after?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is,\Nwe need to take action immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Shirakawa here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruriko,\Nit's from someone named Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:09:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.19,0:10:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:07.55,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Forget that and listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:10.10,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,You should probably\Nstay out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:11.47,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Leave everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm doing pretty\Nwell, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Machiko. Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never take it\Noff, even in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This jewel will protect\Nyou, Machiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll protect\Nyou, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't start with me, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:23.47,Bumper Episode 2-13,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\pos(355,520)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's got you\Nlooking so serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't disturb a great\Ndetective while she's thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo had the same\Nscowl on his face before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He just drank his\Ncoffee and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're searching for\Nsomething in a hurry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have invented\Nsomething Shocker wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Machiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I put... in her locket...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I invented a laser of\Nsuch terrifying power...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's happening...\Nexactly what I was worried about!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nasty business...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Human bodies reduced\Nto just their bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker altered the laser you\Nmade into a weapon, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I never should have put the\Nmicrofilm into that locket.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Machiko is dead, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about Shocker's usual MO.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not going to be satisfied\Nwith two or three deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For our next stage, we're going\Nto expand the scope of the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy a plane with that laser.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Make the world's skies the\Nsole domain of Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need the aid of Shirakawa\Nto create a device that powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring Shirakawa to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Machiko must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up hope yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,As Shocker ramps up\Ntheir evil plans,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'll\Ndecide they need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But... my sister is the most\Nimportant thing in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.73,0:15:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm saying.\NShocker knows that, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill Machiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use that laser to\Nburn her down to her bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to see\Nyour sister's skeleton,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.93,0:16:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,come to the place I'm\Nabout to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:17.52,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,And don't tell Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Shirakawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Shirakawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker called him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be a\Nbuilding around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Once it's finished,\Nyou'll give Machiko back, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish it, and then we'll talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:17:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was doing the pencil\Nscratchings, I got it one street off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She's tracked us down, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:20:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.43,0:21:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now give Machiko back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.21,0:21:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make the Kamen\NRider our guinea pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn your lesson yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the Danger Light will\Nmake quick work of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.98,0:22:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.75,0:22:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Danger Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If scientists don't consider the\Nharm their inventions might do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,they can lead\Nhumankind to tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.55,0:22:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's forget this invention.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.01,0:23:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Machiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.88,0:23:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a wonderful\Nbrother you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:27.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even in times of peace, Takeshi could\Nnot afford to forget Shocker's presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.60,0:23:32.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As long as Shocker was out there, creating\Ncyborgs and plotting world domination,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider Hongo\NTakeshi's battle would continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.37,0:23:40.46,Cont,,570,0,140,,{\blur.8\fad(0,480)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.81,0:23:43.04,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(500.031,486.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.08,0:23:46.43,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(457.419,229.405)}Lizardlon and
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.08,0:23:46.43,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(519,605)}The Monster Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.81,0:23:44.65,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:46.48,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,is Lizardlon and\Nthe monster army.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.81,0:23:51.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker revives the ten monsters\NRider defeated in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.17,0:23:54.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and sends them after Rider\Nled by the powerful Lizardlon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.08,0:23:56.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How will Rider fight them?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.05,0:23:57.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.81,0:23:59.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "Lizardlon and\Nthe Monster Army!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:10.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.43,0:24:13.43,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.43,0:24:15.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.39,0:24:18.43,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.93,0:24:20.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.81,0:24:22.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.69,0:24:24.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.48,0:24:25.82,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.27,0:24:28.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.36,0:24:33.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.03,0:24:37.62,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.62,0:24:41.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.71,0:24:45.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!